Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.80,0:00:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是這麼痛苦的回憶的話 我將不再向他人渴求甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.74,0:00:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十六歲的冬天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.67,0:00:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我體驗了能撕裂身心的痛苦離別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.18,0:01:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,0)}白色花瓣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.86,0:02:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又到聖誕節了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.57,0:02:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我與{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}的初次相遇是在春天的某一日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.42,0:02:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天早晨 我比平常早了很多地來到了學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.02,0:02:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高中二年級的我對甚麼都感到厭煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.64,0:02:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是這個宛如天使牧場的學園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.05,0:02:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是帶著純真微笑的學生們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.90,0:02:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界一定是正確的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.99,0:02:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我就是無法適應它的壞羔羊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.26,0:02:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救這樣的我吧 阿門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.97,0:02:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.17,0:02:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.24,0:02:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼非得和大家一起笑不可？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.55,0:02:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼非得去聽那些毫無興趣的話題不可？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.41,0:02:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我保持著沉默
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.71,0:02:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連做甚麼好或是想去做甚麼也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.53,0:03:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰也別碰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.82,0:03:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的事情全部忘掉吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.08,0:03:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的內心中沒有一絲的滋潤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.94,0:03:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像一個人困在一片乾涸的荒野中無路可走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.67,0:03:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.02,0:03:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶著大人樣的她 看起來全身充滿著我所沒有的滋潤的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.66,0:03:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久保 {\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.20,0:03:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.18,0:03:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我還是第一次聽到\n從你嘴裡冒出別人的名字來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.70,0:03:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.97,0:03:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是今早認識了一個那樣的一年級生而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.65,0:03:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的內心中 有甚麼東西正在開始變化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.93,0:04:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.02,0:04:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖 你作為花蕾的自覺好像太少了一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.46,0:04:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 有稀客在呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.25,0:04:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.47,0:04:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.83,0:04:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為祥子長得跟日本娃娃一樣漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.99,0:04:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不由自主地就想招待她一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.15,0:04:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我長得一副洋味十足的臉孔真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.37,0:04:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 鬧彆扭了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.27,0:04:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜 我喜歡聖的臉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.22,0:04:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說也是憑臉孔選的妹妹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.56,0:04:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實不敢當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.99,0:04:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她曾說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.88,0:04:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「因為我想一直看著這張臉 所以請待在我身邊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.01,0:04:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為這一句話 我決定成為她的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.30,0:04:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我喜歡這樣單純而明快的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.22,0:04:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 從一開始姐姐對待我的方式就非常地高明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.78,0:04:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我變得連自已都吃驚的積極起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.06,0:04:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有甚麼事嗎？ 聖大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.90,0:05:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久保 {\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}同學今天休假了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.64,0:05:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.88,0:05:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想大概在聖堂那裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.99,0:05:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像理所當然似的{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}出現在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.88,0:05:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為被這個世界所愛的潔白而閃耀的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.07,0:05:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貴安 白薔薇的花蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.92,0:05:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.01,0:05:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.08,0:05:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這份心情...會讓你為難嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.99,0:05:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我將自已完全地暴露 追尋著依靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.63,0:05:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經完全不再有退路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.81,0:05:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直想著要見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.76,0:05:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於在這個學園裡能遇見{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.40,0:05:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真想從心裡對神說聲感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.96,0:06:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在可利用的時間裡我們都儘量單獨相處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.46,0:06:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我越來越遠離薔薇館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.02,0:06:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不斷陷入了{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}的那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.59,0:06:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微保持一點距離不是更好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.06,0:06:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.36,0:06:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果想認妹妹 那到也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.51,0:06:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正式地交與念珠 好好地向大家介紹一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.50,0:06:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會考慮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.39,0:06:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我可以走了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.69,0:06:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 一定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.96,0:06:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我並沒有打算認{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}作妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.49,0:06:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐妹的儀式\n是那些沒有像徵就無法安心的人們做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.10,0:06:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從心底嘲笑著這一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.15,0:06:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.33,0:06:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.76,0:07:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概 我們雙方各自都將\n與生俱來的雙手連結到了同一個人的身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.63,0:07:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個結果就是將其它的東西完全地排除在外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.04,0:07:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被說了甚麼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.84,0:07:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明僅此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.15,0:07:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完了嗎？ 游泳的補習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.09,0:07:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.06,0:07:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在事故中喪失了雙親的{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}一直住在學生宿舍裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.86,0:07:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個夏天 {\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}沒有回到長崎的叔叔那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.71,0:07:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是留在了東京的某個修道院裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.57,0:08:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時在這裡避避雨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.71,0:08:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.83,0:08:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒甚麼關係 擦擦你自已的頭髮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.65,0:08:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.87,0:08:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.40,0:09:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼我們 會作為不同的個體出生到這個世上呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.05,0:09:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.48,0:09:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒甚麼 你再睡一會兒也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.90,0:09:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨停了後我會叫醒你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.86,0:09:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.97,0:09:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好癢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.52,0:09:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨啊 別停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.34,0:09:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間就這樣停止好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.07,0:09:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想與{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}溶為一體然後消失掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.46,0:09:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種心情究竟是甚麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.46,0:09:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向自已以外的人渴求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.69,0:09:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這條路的前方又是哪裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.45,0:10:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個答案恐怕永遠也找不到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 即使這樣也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.25,0:10:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最真實的東西只有{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}的悸動 體溫和吐息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.91,0:10:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而這些就是我所期望的這個世界的全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.47,0:10:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的心中{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}的存在膨脹得越來越大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.55,0:10:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在薔薇館的時間變得越來越少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.59,0:10:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.98,0:10:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 聖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.92,0:10:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾也想和你一起喝喝茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.96,0:10:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.26,0:10:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.08,0:11:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斷絕與我的姐妹之緣 重新找一個妹妹如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.55,0:11:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.61,0:11:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要違反約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.15,0:11:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我畢業以前 你可要好好地待在我身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.75,0:11:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使你不認妹妹 那也沒甚麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.50,0:11:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走你自已不會後悔的路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.26,0:11:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又甚麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在等我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.94,0:11:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擺出那副表情嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.14,0:11:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來就像我是瘟神一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.76,0:11:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是說教嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.85,0:11:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微冷靜一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.94,0:11:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明對我們的事甚麼也不知道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.65,0:11:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你又知道{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}同學甚麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.96,0:11:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「甚麼」是指...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.54,0:11:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得還是不要陷得太深為好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.61,0:11:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼要特意來說這種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.30,0:11:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我不想看到你受傷的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.08,0:11:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會受傷？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.83,0:11:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她如果不在了你會怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.62,0:12:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}會...不在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.33,0:12:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你甚麼都沒聽到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.88,0:12:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.53,0:12:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}同學畢業後會進入修道院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.49,0:12:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要成為修女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.41,0:12:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.05,0:12:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.26,0:12:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.83,0:12:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.71,0:12:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在進入這間學校之前就已經決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.50,0:12:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼要隱瞞到現在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.54,0:12:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是沒有機會說而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.68,0:12:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說了也不會有甚麼改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.61,0:12:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我雖然很喜歡{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.51,0:12:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你卻不喜歡我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.53,0:12:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會...！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.82,0:12:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是個畢業前的陪伴… 你是這樣隨便地考慮的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.91,0:13:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡聖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.88,0:13:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會這麼喜歡一個人也是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.60,0:13:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼為甚麼要成為修女甚麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.06,0:13:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起我 你寧願選擇神嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.76,0:13:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是只有{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.05,0:13:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要拋棄我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要像那樣逼問我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.20,0:13:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為修女是我的願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.86,0:13:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼為甚麼不敢看著我的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.60,0:13:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是在迷惑嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.06,0:13:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.52,0:13:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r} 我喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.31,0:13:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.43,0:13:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖母瑪莉亞在看著我們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.85,0:13:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}的回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.89,0:13:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我輸給了聖母瑪莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.81,0:13:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的上課態度變得失常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.77,0:14:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結業式的那天 我受到傳喚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.29,0:14:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.91,0:14:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟她已經再沒有甚麼關係了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.55,0:14:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐藤同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.45,0:14:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久保 {\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}也是這樣說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.81,0:14:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是自已的錯之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.81,0:14:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}也被叫來這裡了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.36,0:14:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一頭陷入一樣東西中而看不清周圍 不是一件很寂寞的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.33,0:14:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}兩日前提出了外宿申請 無論在宿舍還是修道院都找不到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.37,0:14:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r} 怎樣才能見到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.26,0:14:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.98,0:14:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖誕節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.41,0:14:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.14,0:14:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在薔薇館會開一個聯歡會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.57,0:14:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令會為大家做好吃的餅乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.88,0:14:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有心情的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.74,0:14:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們等著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.47,0:14:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r} 好想見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.69,0:15:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想見你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.74,0:15:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.82,0:15:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在見不著你的時候 我只是想著你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.67,0:15:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使做祈禱 也沒法讓你的樣子離開腦海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.27,0:15:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學園長非常擔心我們的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.31,0:15:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也做過約定不再見面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.85,0:15:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.76,0:15:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r} 一起逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.83,0:15:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.83,0:15:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在未知的土地上 不被任何人打擾的活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.66,0:15:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.99,0:15:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不願意嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.23,0:15:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會不願意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.67,0:16:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要和聖在一起 到哪裡都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.45,0:16:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.75,0:16:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.43,0:16:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收拾好行李就過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.13,0:16:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在車站等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.06,0:16:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.14,0:16:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待會兒見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.12,0:16:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}微笑著目送我而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.39,0:16:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無法忘記那個微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.63,0:16:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不會忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.45,0:16:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約定的時間已過去3小時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.51,0:17:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}已經不會來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.76,0:17:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我仍無法離開月台的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.00,0:17:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是無法捨棄也許{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}\n馬上就會從那個樓梯下來的僅有的一點希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.47,0:17:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是做夢 我也想見到{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.86,0:17:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.80,0:17:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.85,0:17:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.81,0:17:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我代替{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}同學來接你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.80,0:17:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}同學好像不會與你一起走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.03,0:17:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.58,0:17:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}同學好像曾經來過這個車站一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.55,0:17:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從遠處注視著在月台上的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.31,0:18:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後覺得果然還是不能這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.66,0:18:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然來了為甚麼不直接...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.45,0:18:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見面後會讓決心變弱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.98,0:18:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變弱？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.45,0:18:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然她看起來很有大人樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.02,0:18:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但畢竟仍只是高中一年級生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.33,0:18:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會動搖也是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.87,0:18:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.25,0:18:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}會去哪裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.26,0:18:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 聽說會轉學到很遠的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.09,0:18:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是她接受了的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.70,0:18:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.28,0:18:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.44,0:18:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒有遇見我的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.70,0:18:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠相遇是件好事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.83,0:18:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能創造可以坦然回想著\n「能夠相遇真好」的未來 那麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.57,0:18:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種未來一定無法來臨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.02,0:18:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷痕總有一天會瘉合的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.54,0:18:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 你不是還有我在身邊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.73,0:18:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會是真以為我只愛著你的臉孔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.71,0:18:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.33,0:18:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是失禮 那只是為了不增加你負擔的一個方便的借口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.81,0:19:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對待你的方式可是很高明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.80,0:19:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.77,0:19:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是姐姐不是就要畢業了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.90,0:19:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會擔心你的可不只是我一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.18,0:19:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.99,0:19:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你擔心真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.02,0:19:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.63,0:19:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是令做的餅乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.96,0:19:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.51,0:19:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.72,0:19:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.77,0:19:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.23,0:19:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才已經向聖的母親打了電話說你要住下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.88,0:19:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.72,0:19:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閒話少說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.17,0:19:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從明天開始就是開心的寒假了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.84,0:19:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就玩到深夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安安靜靜地鬧它一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.16,0:19:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日期已經變了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.83,0:19:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.29,0:19:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.72,0:20:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖誕前夜過去 我知道自己已是十七歲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.15,0:20:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見 {\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.16,0:20:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.29,0:20:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.75,0:20:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.08,0:20:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白薔薇大人也來幫忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.35,0:20:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.41,0:20:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.33,0:20:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日誠子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.83,0:20:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 也就是須加星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.02,0:20:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去大波斯菊編緝部時 曾見過面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.14,0:20:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.15,0:20:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉前段時間失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.42,0:20:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.22,0:20:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的學生給您添了不少麻煩真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.30,0:20:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.74,0:20:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是佐藤 聖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.14,0:21:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 你就是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.60,0:21:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問 今天是...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.14,0:21:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來見學園長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.12,0:21:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那麼 我來為您帶路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.60,0:21:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 我知道路的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.66,0:21:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟過去一點也沒變啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.82,0:21:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 貴安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人是...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.45,0:21:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉安的畢業生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.83,0:21:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 據說已知道香織還活著的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.21,0:21:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是要在聖誕前夜去見香織的
